# Butter Chicken

## Ingredients

- Chicken
- Butter
- Cinnamon
- Turmeric
- Ginger Paste
- Garlic Paste
- Tomatoes
- Water
- Garam Masala
- Cardamom
- Vegetable oil
- Onions


## Instructions

- Marinate the chicken as you please
- Let the chicken settle for 1hr in the freezer
- Preheat the oil in a pan
- Add the whole spices to the oil and let it cook
- After some time add onions and ginger garlic paste
- Add the chicken to the pan in low heat and cook for 30 mins
- Add butter and everything else
- You have Butter Chicken
